│ instructions, we prevent the unsafe reassociation that causes the           │
│ transformation to introduce poison. This ensures that when a trunc          │
│ instruction has the `nsw` flag, the pass will not attempt to distribute it  │
│ through the addition, preserving the original semantics and avoiding the    │
│ creation of poison values."})                                               │
